Welcome to The Whoot!
 
The Whoot is an information feed that bridges the gap between your scattered social circle and plans for the night. Forget the tedious text and tiresome phone-call exercises to figure out who’s staying in and who’s going out. Logon to The Whoot and skip to what’s really important: enjoying your night.
 
Why use The Whoot?
- Easily browse your friends’ plans for the night

- Spread the word about your event by posting an Open Invitation to all your friends

- Anonymously Ping a friend to let them know one of their followers is interested in their plans

- Discover what's trending tonight in your network and city

There is no better way to plan your night than by using The Whoot!